To install:

1. Find your Geany filedefs folder
	* Windows (7) - C:/Users/[username]/AppData/Roaming/geany/filedefs
	* Ubuntu - /home/[username]/.config/geany/filedefs
	* macOS - /Users/[username]/.config/geany/filedefs
2. Extract the files to this folder
3. Restart Geany
4. Voila! You should have an uber sexy Bespin theme for Geany!

Credits
1. Ported from the Bespin theme for Gedit
2. Original Bespin theme belongs to Mozilla Labs (I believe)
3. The Geany Online Theme Editor
